---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-[#000F22] border-t border-gray-900 text-[#CBCFD8] pt-16 pb-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">

      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/favicon.png" alt="AFSB" class="w-8 h-8 object-contain shrink-0" />
          <span class="font-sans text-base font-extrabold text-[#FEFFFF] tracking-tight uppercase">Account For Small Business</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-[#CBCFD8]">
          Affordable, reliable accounting and bookkeeping services for small businesses and SMEs in Singapore. Remote operational excellence powered by certified cloud technology.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 pt-2 text-xs">
          <a href="mailto:hello@accountantforsmallbusiness.com" class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#DAA035] shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
            hello@accountantforsmallbusiness.com
          </a>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#DAA035] shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            Mon&ndash;Fri, Singapore business hours (GMT+8)
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Services -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-sans font-semibold text-[#FEFFFF] uppercase tracking-wider">Core Services</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs">
          <li><a href="/accounting-services-singapore/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">Accounting & Bookkeeping Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="/bookkeeping-services-singapore/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">Day-to-day Bookkeeping</a></li>
          <li><a href="/outsource-accounting-services-singapore/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">Outsource Accounting Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="/payroll-services-singapore/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">Payroll with CPF Submission</a></li>
          <li><a href="/financial-statements-singapore/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">Unaudited Financial Statements</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Company -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-sans font-semibold text-[#FEFFFF] uppercase tracking-wider">Company & Guides</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs">
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">About Mehdi Javed (Founder)</a></li>
          <li><a href="/pricing/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">Transparent Pricing Table</a></li>
          <li><a href="/packages/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">Plan Comparison Matrix</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors font-semibold text-[#DAA035]">Small Business Fin-SME Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact/" class="hover:text-[#DAA035] transition-colors">Contact Us</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Scope -->
      <div class="space-y-4 bg-[#0A1628]/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-900">
        <h4 class="text-xs font-mono font-bold text-[#DAA035] uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          Scope of Service
        </h4>
        <p class="text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-[#CBCFD8]">
          We handle core accounting, bookkeeping, year-end financial statement preparation, payroll, and management reporting remotely.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-[#CBCFD8] border-t border-gray-800/80 pt-2 italic">
          <strong>Compliance Boundary:</strong> We do not act as local filing controllers, file GST, file corporate tax, incorporate companies, or conduct audits. Those services are referred to your licensed filing agent or ACRA-registered public accountant.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom -->
    <div class="border-t border-gray-900 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs">
      <div class="text-center sm:text-left space-y-1">
        <p class="text-[#CBCFD8]">&copy; {year} Account for Small Business LTD &bull; All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-600 font-mono">Designed for remote operational agility using SFRS compliance parameters.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="text-[11px] text-[#CBCFD8]">SFRS & SFRS for Small Entities Compliant</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
